
%h1 Unicycling Society/Federation Membership Management

= link_to "Export Details (excel)", export_organization_memberships_path(format: :xls)

%ul
  %li To update the membership number, click on their Membership Number
  %li If this person has paid via club/etc, and you can confirm it via membership data, ensure that the member number is up-to-date, and then choose "Mark as Confirmed"

%table.memberships.sortable
  %thead
    %tr
      %th ID
      %th Unicycling Membership#
      %th First Name
      %th Last Name
      %th Age
      %th Birthday
      %th City
      %th State
      %th Country
      %th Club
      %th Confirmed?
      %th Actions

  %tbody
    - cache [Registrant, @config] do
      - @registrants.find_each(batch_size: 100) do |reg|
        = render partial: "member_row", object: reg
